module-whatis       "Software package for computing the local resolution of 3D density maps studied in structural biology"
module-url          "https://resmap.sourceforge.net/"
module-license      "CC BY-NC-ND 3.0"
module-maintainer   "João Pedro Agostinho de Sousa <joao.agostinho-de-sousa@psi.ch>"

module-help         "
ResMap (Resolution Map) is a Python (NumPy/SciPy) application with a Tkinter
GUI. It is an easy to use software package for computing the local resolution
of 3D density maps studied in structural biology, primarily electron
cryo-microscopy (cryo-EM).
"

